prometheus server运行
docker run -d -p 9090:9090 -v /data/prometheus/prometheus.yml:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml prom/prometheus

##also to mount your local prometheus.yml on /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml

node_explorer 运行
##offical advice expose 9100
docker run -d --net="host"  --pid="host" --cap-add=SYS_TIME  quay.io/prometheus/node-exporter


grafana运行
docker run -d -p 3000:3000 --name=grafana -v /data/grafana:/var/lib/grafana grafana/grafana

